sentences.pinyin: Zhè gè rén de qiángdù hěn dà.
sentences.translation: This person has a lot of strength.

sentences.simplifiedText: 任何工作，只有用充足的强度去做，才能做得好。
sentences.traditionalText: 任何工作，只有用充足的強度去做，才能做得好。
sentences.pinyin: Rènhé gōngzuò, zhǐyǒu yòng chōngzú de qiángdù qù zuò, cáinéng zuò dé hǎo.
sentences.translation: Any work, only by doing it with sufficient strength, can be done well.
